overview: Jacqui MacCarthy is responsible for business operations. Jacqui is a seasoned online executive, alternating over the past 15 years between product management and sales. Jacqui has in-depth experience in delivering accurate actionable online intelligence to professionals at the world’s leading corporations. Jacqui began her career as a financial analyst for Time Life Books in London, before taking 3 years out to explore Asia. Jacqui attnded Liverpool University and the London College of Distributive Trades where she earned her business degree.
